text: Arsène Lucchini (born 18 September 1922) was a French ski jumper. He competed in the individual event at the 1948 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1922 births Category:Possibly living people Category:French male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of France Category:Ski jumpers at the 1948 Winter Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
